This paper deals with the problem of validating XML documents, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of streaming algorithms also suggests a connection to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the study of space complexity and lower bounds points to the area of computational complexity (cs.CC).
